text: Imre Nagy (7 May 1941 - 24 May 2011) was a Canadian fencer. He competed in the team sabre event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Canadian male fencers Category:Hungarian emigrants to Canada Category:Olympic fencers of Canada Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cluj-Napoca
